\"Attendance Okay\" (hereinafter referred as \"app\") is an effort to ease out the process of marking daily attendance on the portal.

The app does not collect any personal information or data. It saves your login credentials for the \'employee self service portal\' on your device only. If the data from the app is cleared or the app is uninstalled, the data gets cleared in the process.

Other than your correct login credentials which are required for logon to the ess portal, the app does not require any special permission from you to work.

This app is not linked with troubleshooting your issues related to ESS portal as such and you are required to use already established channels to address so.

Contact for any query at:<\br> amarpreet.rites@gmail.com
Login details saved. To change/update go to app settings
